==== SOURCE

https://towardsdatascience.com/recommender-systems-in-practice-cef9033bb23a

==== AGENT

Netflix.

==== GOAL

Improve movie/tv-series recommendations for its users.

==== DATA

Based on the users historial data of watched content.

==== METHODS

Implement collaborative filtering which makes recommendations based on historic users' preference for items i.e. clicked, watch, purchased, liked, rated etc. 

==== RESULTS

They were able to provide more accurate content recommendations for its users.

==== COMMENTS

Alike Spotify, useful if a user wants to watch content of a similar genre.